title: Tambovenergo is ready for the autumn-winter peak demand (IDGC of Centre JSC)
text: ( Source : IDGC of Centre JSC ) 02.10. 2015 2 October 2015 IDGC of Centre - Tambovenergo division held a meeting of the interdepartmental commission for assessing the readiness of the enterprise for the autumn-winter operation period ( AWP ).
